This paper deals with natural language processing in source code, specifically identifying subtokens in source code identifiers. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the Software Engineering (cs.SE) category. However, it also uses machine learning techniques, which could place it in the categories of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Programming Languages (cs.PL), or Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI).
